Package org.gradle.api.artifacts.cache

Classes for controlling dependency resolution.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ArtifactResolutionControl Command methods for controlling artifact resolution via the DSL.
    DependencyResolutionControl Command methods for controlling dependency resolution via the DSL.
    ModuleResolutionControl Command methods for controlling module resolution via the DSL.
    ResolutionControl Command methods for controlling dependency resolution via the DSL.
    ResolutionRules Represents a set of rules/actions that can be applied during dependency resolution.
